    <note>Chen(1) Qiu [19810] See documentation for son-in-law, Deng(1) Li [19804]. I am asuming that he was at least a lineage cousin of Chen(1) Liu [19799], probably the father of Chen(1) G [19811] and, therefore, grandfather of Guangdao(2) [19813] and Guangyuan(2) [19812]. G's wife was probably a daughter of Deng(1) Yi [19807], thereby establishing a very good example of cross-cousin marrage, Even if the exact relationships are incorrect, the Deng(1) are almost certainly members of the same lineage as were the Chen(1).</note>
